one mistake, which was we

00:02:30.350 --> 00:02:32.660
left out all this stuff
that's called dark matter.

00:02:32.660 --> 00:02:34.910
And then that discovery I
told you about a minute ago,

00:02:34.910 --> 00:02:36.576
where there was the
acceleration instead

00:02:36.576 --> 00:02:38.205
